-{SEGA}- CD版《午夜陷阱》的评价最初褒贬不一。值得注意的是，该游戏是-{SEGA}- CD平台的首部互动式电影，因此被认为是游戏类型及技术层面的新突破<ref name="segaforce">{{cite journal|date=June 1993|title=Night Trap|journal=Sega Force|issue=18|pages=64–66}}</ref><ref name="mms">{{cite journal|date=April 1993|title=Night Trap|journal=Mean Machines Sega|issue=7|pages=60–63}}</ref>。评论人很快便指出游戏的[[B级片|B级片]]质感使人想起青少年恐怖片<ref name="mms" /><ref name="Dragon195">{{cite journal |last2=Lesser |first2=Patricia |last3=Lesser |first3=Kirk |date=July 1993 |title=The Role of Computers |url=https://annarchive.com/files/Drmg195.pdf |journal=Dragon |issue=195 |pages=58 |last1=Lesser |first1=Hartley |lastauthoramp=yes |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321120257/http://annarchive.com/files/Drmg195.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-21 |access-date=2020-09-09 }}</ref><ref name="ElectronicGames">{{cite journal|last=Camron|first=Marc|date=December 1992|title=Night Trap|url=https://archive.org/stream/Electronic-Games-1992-12/Electronic%20Games%201992-12#page/n97/mode/2up|journal=Electronic Games|volume=1|issue=3|page=99|accessdate=2015-03-23|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408140642/https://archive.org/stream/Electronic-Games-1992-12/Electronic%20Games%201992-12|archivedate=2015-04-08}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Sega Force|Sega Force}}》的编辑认为，玩这个游戏就像是“导演你自己的B级片。《午夜陷阱》让你身临其境<ref name="segaforce" />。”评论员表示，“古怪”、“低俗”的幽默感帮助提升游戏的吸引力，增强魅力<ref name="segaforce" /><ref name="Dragon195" /><ref name="ElectronicGames" />。从技术层面来看，尽管世嘉CD的色彩表现较弱，游戏的画面还是被表扬质量高、顺滑<ref name="mms" /><ref name="Dragon195" /><ref name="segazone">{{cite journal|last=|first=|date=June 1993|title=Night Trap|url=|journal=Sega Zone|volume=|issue=8|pages=30–31|via=}}</ref>。游戏玩法是最常被人投诉的地方。部分评论人认为玩法无聊、肤浅，基本上是在合适的时间按下按钮诱捕敌人<ref name="segaforce" /><ref name="cvg">{{cite journal|last=|first=|date=|title=Night Trap|url=|journal=Computer and Video Games|volume=|issue=138|pages=70–71|via=}}</ref>。《[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]》的职员认为《午夜陷阱》类似于《[[龍穴歷險記|龍穴歷險記]]》（1983）和《{{tsl|en|Space Ace|王牌空军}}》，玩法上存在同样的问题，都是在合适的时机按下按钮<ref name="cvg" />。

游戏移植到其他平台的版本收到更为严苛的评价。评论员认为移植的改良不是很好。《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》认为移植版“某种程度上有所创新，但画面和音效如今玩起来像是很普通的东西”<ref name="GamePro">{{cite journal|last=|first=|date=March 1994|title=ProReview: Night Trap|journal=GamePro|publisher=IDG|issue=56|page=118}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|GameFan|GameFan}}》的评论人批评游戏铺天盖地的宣传使得作品让人感觉比实际要好，表示“这就是一款一般的游戏，不过是获得太多不合理的关注而已<ref name="GameFan">{{cite magazine|last=|first=|date=February 1994|title=Night Trap|url=|magazine=GameFan|volume=2|issue=3|pages=19, 110}}</ref>。”评论人一边道认为游戏无聊乏味<ref name="ngen">{{cite magazine|date=May 1995|title=32X Ratings: Night Trap|magazine=Next Generation|issue=5|page=91}}</ref><ref name="GameFan" /><ref name="edge">{{cite magazine|date=March 1994|title=Night Trap review (3DO)|url=http://www.edge-online.com/review/night-trap-review/|issue=6|author=Edge staff|magazine=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531022631/http://www.edge-online.com/review/night-trap-review/|archivedate=2013-05-31|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2015-07-30}}</ref>。《[[次世代|次世代]]》认为游戏“是有史以来最让人觉得崩溃的无聊作品......它就不是游戏<ref name="ngen" />。”评论人同意3DO和32X版本比-{SEGA}- CD原版呈现了更多的颜色及更高质量的视频<ref name="ngen" /><ref name="GPro69">{{cite magazine|last=|first=|date=April 1995|title=ProReview: Night Trap|magazine=GamePro|publisher=IDG|issue=69|page=60}}</ref><ref name="GameFan" /><ref name="edge" />。《午夜陷阱》在商业上获得成功，截至1998年共售出40万份<ref name=nextgen>{{cite magazine |author=Kent, Steve|magazine=Next Generation | title=Retroview | issue=38 | date=February 1998 |page=37}}</ref>。

游戏后来被人回归时依然获得负面的评价，最为人熟知的地方基本上是所衍生的争议。2001年，游戏被《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》编辑{{tsl|en|Seanbaby|Seanbaby}}列为史上第12糟糕游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.seanbaby.com/nes/nes/egm12.htm |title=EGM's Crapstravaganza: The 20 Worst Games of All Time (#12: Night Trap) |publisher=Seanbaby.com |accessdate=2017-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020605051837/http://www.seanbaby.com/nes/egm12.htm |archivedate=2002-06-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年，他和其他游戏记者在介绍荒诞劣质游戏的网络系列喜剧节目《{{tsl|en|Broken Pixels|坏像素}}》中介绍了这款游戏<ref name="gamevideos.1up.com">{{cite web |url=http://gamevideos.1up.com/video/id/11240 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707061839/http://gamevideos.1up.com/video/id/11240 |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2011-07-07 |title=Broken Pixels Episode 08 from GameVideos |publisher=Gamevideos.1up.com |date=2007-05-04 |accessdate=2009-08-21 }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Yahoo! Games|雅虎游戏}}于2007年将游戏列入史上最具争议性游戏榜单，表示：“如果不是因为它的争议，这款一次性-{SEGA}- CD游戏会逐渐被人遗忘，只因为这款游戏是将游戏玩法与真人视频相结合的又一次失败尝试<ref>{{cite web |title=Controversial Games |publisher=Yahoo! Games |author=Ben Silverman |date=2007-09-17 |url=http://videogames.yahoo.com/feature/controversial-games/530593 |accessdate=2007-09-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070922155732/http://videogames.yahoo.com/feature/controversial-games/530593 |archivedate=2007-09-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。”《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》2008年将游戏列入最差恐怖游戏名单<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Juba|first=Joe|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2012/10/31/the-wrong-kind-of-scary-worst-horror-games-ever.aspx|title=The Wrong Kind of Scary: Worst Horror Games Ever|magazine=Game Informer|date=October 2008|issue=186|page=121|accessdate=2017-07-21|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728173227/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2012/10/31/the-wrong-kind-of-scary-worst-horror-games-ever.aspx|archivedate=2017-07-28}}</ref>。2014年，游戏位列[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]100个最差游戏榜单第59位，被认为“不像游戏，更像对耐心的考验”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/worst-games-all-time/ |title=The 100 worst games of all time |publisher=GamesRadar |date=2015-05-01 |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702102752/http://www.gamesradar.com/worst-games-all-time/ |archivedate=2014-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1996年，《[[电脑游戏世界|电脑游戏世界]]》将游戏列入史上50款最差游戏榜单的第6位，认为游戏中“全动态影像的最终体验很差”<ref name=cgw150>{{cite magazine |author=Staff |url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/issues/cgw_148.pdf |title=150 Best (and 50 Worst) Games of All Time |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=November 1996 |issue=148 |page=88 |accessdate=2017-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511185822/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/issues/cgw_148.pdf |archivedate=2013-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==再版发行==
2014年5月，《午夜陷阱》设计者詹姆斯·莱利宣布正就分辨率及玩法有所改进的再发行版进行商讨<ref name="Polygon: rerelease" />。同年8月，成立了Night Trap有限公司的游戏原作者发起[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]众筹活动<ref name="Revamped">{{cite web |last1=McElroy |first1=Justin |title=Night Trap ReVamped aims to reanimate the FMV classic via Kickstarter |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/11/5990633/night-trap-revamped-fmv |website=Polygon |accessdate=2014-08-11 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813222323/http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/11/5990633/night-trap-revamped-fmv |archivedate=2014-08-13 }}</ref>，若目标达成将会重新发行其他Digital Pictures作品。另外，公司也在考虑制作原版游戏的续集<ref name="Revamped" />。最终结果未达预期，33万美元的目标只得到了39843美元<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1018579240/night-trap-revamped#|title=Night Trap ReVamped|website=Kickstarter-US|access-date=2017-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321060400/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1018579240/night-trap-revamped|archive-date=2017-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

两年后的2016年5月，游戏开发者泰勒·霍格（Tyler Hogle）制作了《午夜陷阱》智能手机版的{{tsl|en|Technology demonstration|技术演示}}。他此前曾参与《{{tsl|en|Double Switch (video game)|双重开关}}》（1993）和《{{tsl|en|Quarterback Attack with Mike Ditka|与迈克·迪特卡四分卫进攻|四分卫进攻}}》（1995）两部Digital Pictures游戏的移植。他在网上匿名发布了《午夜陷阱》演示版的短视频，促使部分游戏网站报道该视频，并询问汤姆·齐托有没有参与计划。霍格的确联系了齐托，两人正开发完整的作品。原版源代码及1987年影片的母带遗失，但莱利拥有已经定好时间的母带画面，便把它交给霍格。由于画面已经调好时间，霍格开发起来就更加容易了。然而，他还是要将原版游戏玩上几遍，才能找到触发场景的动作<ref name="mlig" />。

为纪念游戏发行25周年，名为《午夜陷阱：25周年版》（''Night Trap: 25th Anniversary Edition''）于2017年公布<ref name=announce/>。游戏于2017年8月15日在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]平台发行，[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]版计划于未来发行<ref name="kotau"/>。游戏由霍格的Screaming Villains开发发行，而限量实体版则由{{tsl|en|Limited Run Games|Limited Run Games}}面向PlayStation 4发行，共有三个封面，仿照当年世嘉CD原版、后来的世嘉CD版及32X版的封面<ref name=announce>{{cite web|last1=Romano|first1=Sal|title=Night Trap: 25th Anniversary Edition announced for PS4, Xbox One|url=http://gematsu.com/2017/04/night-trap-25th-anniversary-edition-announced-ps4-xbox-on|website=Gematsu|accessdate=2017-04-25|date=2017-04-25|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909175127/https://www.gematsu.com/2017/04/night-trap-25th-anniversary-edition-announced-ps4-xbox-one|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://limitedrungames.com/blogs/news/night-trap-watch-out-behind-you|title=Night Trap! Watch out behind you!|last=|first=|date=|work=Limited Run Games|access-date=2017-05-07|archive-date=2017-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170605084001/https://limitedrungames.com/blogs/news/night-trap-watch-out-behind-you|dead-url=no}}</ref>。娱乐软件分级委员会给予再版“青少年”级评价，比原版的“成年”评级要低<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ponder|first1=Stacie|title=25 Years Later, 'Disgusting' Night Trap Is Incredibly Tame|url=https://kotaku.com/25-years-later-disgusting-night-trap-is-incredibly-tam-1797864067|website=Kotaku|accessdate=2017-09-28|date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928193409/https://kotaku.com/25-years-later-disgusting-night-trap-is-incredibly-tam-1797864067|archive-date=2017-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。周年纪念版采用了未压缩的图像，并新增此前未收录的一个开场和一个丹尼的死亡镜头、幕后开发人员评述、观看所有剧情视频的“剧院模式”、昂格斯族在房子中不断冒出的“幸存者模式”以及《犯罪现场》的可玩版<ref name="mlig" /><ref name="kotau">{{cite web|last=Walker|first=Alex|title=Of All Things, Night Trap Comes Out Next Month|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2017/07/of-all-things-night-trap-comes-out-next-month/|work=Kotaku|accessdate=2017-07-29|date=2017-07-29|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728020354/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2017/07/of-all-things-night-trap-comes-out-next-month/|archivedate=2017-07-28}}</ref>。

游戏[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]版于2018年8月24日发行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/08/13/night-trap-official-digital-release-date-nintendo-switch/ |title=Night Trap Gets Official Digital Release Date For Nintendo Switch |date=2018-08-13 |website=Comicbook |access-date=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815024308/https://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/08/13/night-trap-official-digital-release-date-nintendo-switch/ |archive-date=2018-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多位记者指出，讽刺的是，前[[任天堂|任天堂]]美国总裁霍华德·林肯曾在1993年的国会听证会上宣称“《午夜陷阱》永远不会出现在任天堂的平台”<ref>{{cite web|last1=McWhertor|first1=Michael|title=Nintendo once vowed Night Trap would never be on its systems, but things change|url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/4/20/17263846/nintendo-night-trap-howard-lincoln-congress|website=Polygon|date=2018-04-20|access-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421142919/https://www.polygon.com/2018/4/20/17263846/nintendo-night-trap-howard-lincoln-congress|archive-date=2018-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏还发行了[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]版<ref>{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/10/28/night-trap-25th-anniversary-edition-coming-ps-vita/ |title=‘Night Trap: 25th Anniversary Edition’ Creeping Its Way To PlayStation Vita |date=2018-10-28 |publisher=Comicbook |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181126221433/https://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/10/28/night-trap-25th-anniversary-edition-coming-ps-vita/ |archive-date=2018-11-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://limitedrungames.com/products/limited-run-193-night-trap-vita |title=LIMITED RUN #193: NIGHT TRAP CLASSIC EDITION (VITA) |access-date=2019-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210248/https://limitedrungames.com/products/limited-run-193-night-trap-vita |archive-date=2019-01-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

